# Anthropic API key — used to extract absence reasons from the Congressional
# Record and to summarize the daily floor agenda. Without it, the pipeline
# still runs: absences are detected from roll-call data, reasons show as
# "Undisclosed". Get one at https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Congress.gov API key (free) — optional fallback source for House votes and
# the Congressional Record. The pipeline prefers no-key sources (Senate LIS
# XML, House Clerk XML, govinfo bulk data). Sign up at https://api.congress.gov/
CONGRESS_GOV_API_KEY=
